parameters: \n<Therapist><WordWrap>Hey, I got a quick tip for you before we have our talk later.

\n<Therapist><WordWrap>Our grief can easily become a slippery slope of negative emotions. It'll seem hard to keep your balance as you slide from one thought to the next. It's important to remind yourself that there were happy times too and those don't suddenly go away.
\n<Therapist><WordWrap>Some items can remind you of those memories and help you get a grip on your situation. Maybe look for one of those items to help?
